text: Irena Szydłowska (28 January 1928 - 14 August 1983) was a Polish archer. Szydłowska competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics and the 1976 Summer Olympics.Irena Szydłowska == References == Category:1928 births Category:1983 deaths Category:Polish archers Category:Olympic silver medalists for Poland
